      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_02_aoi/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_02_aoi-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "やぁ。ちょっといいかな\n僕らの合宿の話、聞いた？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey. Can I talk to you for a moment?\nHave you heard\nabout our training camp?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.8666666667000005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_02_aoi/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_02_aoi-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "…変な反応だね。でもそう\n久しぶりに四人で合宿だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Your reaction is strange. But yes‚\nIt's been a while since the four of us\nhad a camp together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.0666666667,
      "endTime": 13.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_02_aoi/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_02_aoi-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "こころのことだ。何を考えて\nいるのか分からない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm worried about Kokoro.\nI don't know\nwhat she's thinking.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.7,
      "endTime": 18.071859359799998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_02_aoi/sud_vo_adv_event_2208_02_aoi-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "何かあったらマネージャーの\n責任、だからね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If something happens‚\nit's the manager's\nresponsibility‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
